How to choose the right attorneyFind an attorney in Houston, TX713-779-8500Our dedicated focus to providing the utmost of personal attention to each of our clients separates us from many larger firms. Meet our attorney






The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C.At The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C., we understand that for many, there is a level of uncertainty or anxiety with simply needing to meet with the attorney for the first time. Our goal is to remove any worries you may have and to give each of our clients the comfort of knowing their case is protected and being handled professionally while minimizing the interruption of their daily lives.  From the initial interview through the final resolution, your case is thoroughly prepared with the mind set that someday, it may be presented to a Judge or Jury by an attorney. 






Personal AttentionPersonal attention to client satisfaction is what separates The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C., from other personal injury law firms. At The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C. in Houston, TX, you receive personal attention in meeting and dealing with a board certified attorney from the initial interview through the conclusion of your case, rather than being lateraled to a paralegal. You receive personal attention knowing you can call any time and discuss the status of your case, with your lawyer. You receive personal attention beginning to completion and your file will only be closed after all legal contingencies are resolved and resolution is complete to all legal matters. Personal attention is what you deserve and what you can expect as a client of The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C.




















