Auto Accidents







Have You Been Injured in an Auto Accident?Contact a trusted personal injury lawyer in Houston, TX If you’ve been injured in an auto accident, your life has been turned upside down. Everything is different. You’re dealing with an injury. You have a totaled car. Now, you have to deal with the insurance company and the other party. Make sure that you have the right attorney on your side to protect you during this process. At The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C., we offer outstanding support for injured individuals in Houston, Texas. Our attorney has represented hundreds of individuals after an auto accident. Whether you want to fight for damages or simply need legal advice, our attorney is here to help.




Steering you in the right directionAn accident can occur in a number of different ways. No matter the circumstances, our attorney will protect you and fight for your rights until the dust has settled. Work with an attorney who has experience in all of the following: Auto defect accidentsMotorcycle accidentsBicycle and pedestrian accidentsRear-end collisionsHead-on collisionsSUV rolloversBus crashesDrunk driving accidentsTexting and cellphone accidentsCollisions at intersectionsFires from car crashesYou may be down, but you’re not out. Trust an experienced auto accident attorney in Houston, Texas to help you get back on your feet. Reach out to The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C. today to discuss your case. 








