Workplace Injuries







You Could Be Entitled to Workers CompensationWork with our personal injury attorney in Houston, TX for your workplace injuryMany Houston residents go to work every day, not thinking about whether or not they will come home with an injury. If you’ve been injured while at work, you may be entitled to workers compensation. Make sure you hire an experienced personal injury attorney to help you with all of the specifics. The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C. helps workers and their families after workplace accidents. Our attorney has worked with employers and insurance agents to obtain justified compensation for clients. When you need the best in your corner, turn to The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C. 




Accidents can occur anywhere, at any timeA workplace injury can happen in any field. Whether you work in an office or on an oil rig, you could get injured while at work. The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C. has worked on a number of injury cases, including those revolving around: Illnesses ElectrocutionsMaritime accidents Workplace burnsConstruction accidents Railroad injuriesAt The Law Offices of David P. Petersen, P.C., it is our duty to help injured people. Schedule a consultation with our attorney today to discuss your case.  








