About
Dr. David Petersen, MD is a Doctor primarily located in Van Nuys, CA, with another office in Mission Hills, CA. He has 27 years of experience. His specialties include General Practice.                    Dr. Petersen is affiliated with                            Monterey Park Hospital,                            Greater El Monte Community Hospital and                            Torrance Memorial Medical Center.
                 He speaks English.



